    "date": "2021-03-26T14:14:18Z",
    "text": "Fairness in Social Security Act of\u00a0 2021\n\nThis bill excludes from modified adjusted gross income, for income tax purposes, any lump-sum social security benefit payment (i.e., a payment of more than one month of social security benefits) that is attributable to months ending before the beginning\u00a0of the taxable year. It also waives any statute of limitation for credits or refunds resulting from this bill."
